{
  "stem": "20021.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Somehow they were very aloof, maybe because of that propaganda, Polish Jews or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But anyhow, to the extent that we met people and could talk to them, we tried to tell them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Look, something has to be done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We have to do something, because what Eichmann-- once Eichmann is here-- when Eichmann came, the first thing he did, he arrested Horthy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Horthy was the ruler of Hungary, the president so to speak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was trying very much to be benevolent to Jews at that time in 1943, to reassure them, and nothing would happen to you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we regret what we did in 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because at first the Hungarians were very bad to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And also, there was-- I forgot the name-- there was a guard there in Hungary, which were very anti-Semitic, Nazi-like sort of.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Horthy was fighting them and preventing them from gaining too much power.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Suddenly when Eichmann came, they got all the power they wanted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And Horthy was basically put into house arrest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was written on the wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things are going to be very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And indeed, they were later very bad for Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what I found very interesting that when we tried to tell Hungarian Jews about it, nobody wanted to believe us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They turned away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you're spreading propaganda.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're scaring people away, this type of stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I immediately went to look, somehow, how to get out of Hungary and go to Romania.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't sure that Romania was much better, but my theory was simply it can't get worse than it's going to get in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Eichmann is here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Eichmann at that time was not known as yet as he's known now, because all what he did was not known.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
